Input:
n = 4
Expected output:
4321
321
21
1
CODE:
class Pattern{
public static void main(String[] args){
int n=4;
for(int i=n;i>=1;i--){
for(int j=i;j>=1;j--){
System.out.print(j);
}
System.out.println();
}
}
}
OUTPUT:
4321
321
21
1

